{
  "stem": "13469.7",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it meant studying in evening classes in Birmingham for something like five years to get this degree from London University in mechanical engineering.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I did this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I worked during the day at BSA Tools.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I studied in the evening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went to technical college four or five days a week to study all the various subjects for this degree.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and I was much occupied by that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and certainly, the Holocaust-- I forgot all about the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never really thought about the Holocaust at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really had-- really very busy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't recollect that, really, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe they asked a few questions of what happened, and that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we never gave them the full story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think they ever knew about the train and all those sort of things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I regret now that we never discussed all these sort of things, because they probably could've filled me in on lots of things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One, my father didn't come to England.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm sure they knew all that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I can only say that I-- first of all, I lived in Birmingham.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and when I first came over, we were, perhaps, reticent to talk to other people about our experiences.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because nobody was interested in those days-- I mean, when Belsen was liberated, it was high profile, so I gather, having seen all the papers and speeches and documentation and all that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But very soon afterwards, the mood, apparently, in Britain changed completely, in that Britain wanted to be friends with the Germans against the Russians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they didn't want to play up the atrocities in the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is the story I've heard.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
